  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So my father wore a uniform in 1938.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you must understand my father always maintained those connections.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so all planning for an uprising started in March of 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I, of course, had no idea about it whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "A meeting took place late in June of 1944 when some of the key generals of the Slovak army decided that they are going to trigger off an uprising and execute the military mission-- let the Russians across the-- across the Carpathian Mountain passes.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There are only three passes through which you really can come in any kind of a massive army with tanks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's, it's, it's a mountainous region.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Communist party was given the job because this was going to be a joint action to maintain the liaison with the Soviet high command-- which by the way was commanded by Khrushchev-- to plan the takeover and plan the coup.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Communist party absolutely did not want to have an uprising by the army because that really means that when they come over there is a nationalist army who are largely beholden to the west.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This is very much the same scenario as what happened in Poland by the way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so, so you have then this plan going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The short story is that the uprising starts prematurely in August 28, 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- my father knew that the uprising would be happening, although he did not know exactly the date.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, I think in mid-August we went into our executed plan, which is go to a certain village up in the mountains and disperse the family and then just hunker down, put on pleasant clothing and so forth.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in that mode for about 10 days, like three days before the uprising.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
